# Strength Deck Core

Vanilla PWA: `index.html` + `styles.css` + `app.js`. No framework, no bundler.

- Storage: `localStorage` key `strength-deck-state-v1`. Never rename without migration.
- State: multi-user `{ users[], activeUserId }`. Always mutate via `activeUser()`, then `saveState()` + `renderAll()`.
- UI language: Korean copy; English eyebrows only (Today, Calendar, My Page).
- Design: dark Spotify-style tokens in `:root`. Accent `#1ed760` only. See `docs/DESIGN-SYSTEM.md`.
- SW cache: bump `CACHE_NAME` in `sw.js` when static assets change.
- Docs: `AGENTS.md` is the entry point; `docs/` has architecture, data model, program logic.

When adding features, reuse `.panel`, `.exercise-card`, `.set-row`, `.badge`, pill buttons — do not invent new visual patterns.
